== 製作 ==
2006年6月，據[[雷利·史考特|雷利·史考特]]將執導一部講述[[古馳|古馳]]家族時尚王朝衰落的電影，由{{le|安德里亞·伯洛夫|Andrea Berloff}}編劇<ref>{{cite web|date=2006-06-21|title=Andrea Berloff To Write Gucci Family Biopic|url=https://movieweb.com/andrea-berloff-to-write-gucci-family-biopic/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506022607/https://movieweb.com/andrea-berloff-to-write-gucci-family-biopic/|archive-date=2019-05-06|access-date=2021-03-01|publisher=[[MovieWeb|MovieWeb]]}}</ref>。2012年2月，雷利·史考特的女兒喬丹·史考特將接替他擔任導演，[[潘妮洛普·克魯茲|潘妮洛普·克魯茲]]為飾演主角{{le|派翠琪亞·雷吉亞尼|Patrizia Reggiani}}進行洽談<ref>{{cite web|last=Keene|first=Allison|date=2012-10-12|title=Ridley Scott's Daughter Replaces Him as Director on Gucci; Penelope Cruz in Talks for Lead|url=https://collider.com/gucci-penelope-cruz-jordan-scott/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421235022/https://collider.com/gucci-penelope-cruz-jordan-scott/|archive-date=2019-04-21|access-date=2021-03-01|work=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]]}}</ref>。2016年11月，[[王家衛|王家衛]]接替喬丹執導電影，[[查爾斯·蘭道夫|查爾斯·蘭道夫]]和伯洛夫撰寫劇本，並考慮由[[瑪格·羅比|瑪格·羅比]]飾演雷吉亞尼<ref>{{cite web|last=Shoard|first=Catherine|date=2016-11-17|title=Wong Kar-Wai to return with Gucci murder movie|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/nov/17/wong-kar-wai-return-maurizio-gucci-fashion-murder-movie|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170301094314/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2016/nov/17/wong-kar-wai-return-maurizio-gucci-fashion-murder-movie|archive-date=2017-03-01|access-date=2021-03-01|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]}}</ref>。2019年11月，再次改由雷利·史考特執導電影，羅伯托·本蒂維尼亞（{{lang|en|Roberto Bentivegna}}）編寫劇本，[[女神卡卡|女神卡卡]]飾演雷吉亞尼<ref>{{cite web|last=Jr|first=Mike Fleming|date=2019-11-01|title=Lady Gaga, Ridley & Giannina Scott Team On Film About Assassination Of Gucci Grandson Maurizio; Gaga To Play Convicted Ex-Wife Patrizia Reggiani|url=https://deadline.com/2019/11/lady-gaga-ridley-scott-movie-maurizio-gucci-patrizia-reggiani-murder-gucci-family-giannina-scott-1202774518/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904022917/https://deadline.com/2019/11/lady-gaga-ridley-scott-movie-maurizio-gucci-patrizia-reggiani-murder-gucci-family-giannina-scott-1202774518/|archive-date=2020-09-04|access-date=2021-03-01|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline]]}}</ref>。2020年4月，[[米高梅|米高梅]]獲得了該片的版權<ref name="MGMGucci">{{Cite web|last=Siegel|first=Tatiana|last2=Kit|first2=Borys|date=2020-04-08|title=MGM Buys Ridley Scott's 'Gucci' Film With Lady Gaga Set to Star (Exclusive)|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mgm-buys-ridley-scotts-gucci-film-lady-gaga-set-star-1289108|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200411063928/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/mgm-buys-ridley-scotts-gucci-film-lady-gaga-set-star-1289108|archive-date=2020-04-11|access-date=2021-03-01|website=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]}}</ref>。2020年8月，[[亞當·崔佛|亞當·崔佛]]、[[傑瑞德·雷托|傑瑞德·雷托]]、[[艾爾·帕西諾|艾爾·帕西諾]]、[[勞勃·狄尼洛|勞勃·狄尼洛]]、[[傑克·休斯頓|傑克·休斯頓]]和[[瑞夫·卡尼|瑞夫·卡尼]]為出演電影進行洽談<ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|date=2020-08-20|title=MGM's Ridley Scott-Lady Gaga Gucci Film Eyes Robert De Niro, Jared Leto, Al Pacino, Adam Driver, Jack Huston & Reeve Carney|url=https://deadline.com/2020/08/mgm-ridley-scott-lady-gaga-gucci-film-robert-de-niro-jared-leto-al-pacino-adam-driver-reeve-carney-1202997254/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822022656/https://deadline.com/2020/08/mgm-ridley-scott-lady-gaga-gucci-film-robert-de-niro-jared-leto-al-pacino-adam-driver-reeve-carney-1202997254/|archive-date=2020-08-22|access-date=2021-03-01|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline]]}}</ref>。2020年10月，確認崔佛、雷托、帕西諾和狄尼洛加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|last=Jr|first=Mike Fleming|date=2020-09-14|title=Ridley Scott Eyes Another Epic: Joaquin Phoenix As Napoleon In 'Kitbag' As Director Today Wraps 'The Last Duel’|url=https://deadline.com/2020/10/ridley-scott-joaquin-phoenix-napoleon-epic-kitbag-wraps-the-last-duel-today-1234597342/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015054250/https://deadline.com/2020/10/ridley-scott-joaquin-phoenix-napoleon-epic-kitbag-wraps-the-last-duel-today-1234597342/|archive-date=2020-09-15|access-date=2021-03-01|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline]]}}</ref>。2020年12月，確認休斯頓和卡尼加入演員陣容，而[[傑瑞米·艾恩斯|傑瑞米·艾恩斯]]接替狄尼洛出演電影<ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|date=2020-12-07|title=Jeremy Irons Joins Lady Gaga In Ridley Scott And MGM's 'Gucci'|url=https://deadline.com/2020/12/jeremy-irons-lady-gaga-ridley-scott-mgms-gucci-1234651575/|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208002055/https://deadline.com/2020/12/jeremy-irons-lady-gaga-ridley-scott-mgms-gucci-1234651575/|archive-date=2020-12-18|access-date=2021-03-01|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Kit|first=Borys|date=2020-12-07|title=Jeremy Irons Joins Lady Gaga in Ridley Scott's 'Gucci'|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jeremy-irons-joins-lady-gaga-in-ridley-scotts-gucci|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201208022941/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/jeremy-irons-joins-lady-gaga-in-ridley-scotts-gucci|archive-date=2020-12-08|access-date=2021-03-01|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]}}</ref>。同月底，宣佈{{le|達魯休·沃爾斯基|Dariusz Wolski}}擔任該片的攝影師<ref>{{cite web|last1=Tangcay|first1=Jazz|title='News of the World' Cinematographer Says 'Everyone Is in the Same Boat' for Streaming Releases|url=https://variety.com/2020/artisans/news/dariusz-wolski-scolds-christopher-nolan-hbo-max-1234866520/|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|access-date=2021-03-02|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125201438/https://variety.com/2020/artisans/news/dariusz-wolski-scolds-christopher-nolan-hbo-max-1234866520/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年1月，[[卡米爾·科坦_(演員)|卡米爾·科坦]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|last=Hoballah|first=Rania|date=2021-01-13|title="Gucci" : Camille Cottin rejoint le casting du film de Ridley Scott|url=https://www.lci.fr/culture/gucci-camille-cottin-rejoint-le-casting-du-film-de-ridley-scott-2175391.html|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202014832/https://www.lci.fr/culture/gucci-camille-cottin-rejoint-le-casting-du-film-de-ridley-scott-2175391.html|archive-date=2021-02-02|access-date=2021-03-01|publisher=[[La_Chaîne_Info|LCI]]|language=fr}}</ref>。

