== 評價 ==
本片在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據355條評論，持有63%的新鮮度，平均得分6.2／10，觀眾投票獲得83%的分數，平均得分為4.2／5；共识评论：“經常在受啟發的陣營和沈悶的戲劇之間搖擺不定，以致無法展現自信的伸展台支柱，但 Lady Gaga 完美的音符表演擁有永恆的風格。”<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/house_of_gucci|title=House of Gucci|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2022-05-10|archive-date=2022-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220428131555/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/house_of_gucci|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[IMDb|IMDb]]則獲得6.6/10的平均分數<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11214590/|title=House of Gucci|3=|website=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|accessdate=2022-05-10|archive-date=2022-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220508231750/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt11214590/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，電影根據57條專業評論，獲得59分（滿分100分），代表「褒貶不一或中庸」。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/house-of-gucci|title=House of Gucci|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2022-05-10|archive-date=2022-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418212108/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/house-of-gucci|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在[[第42屆金酸莓獎|第42屆金酸莓獎]]上，參演本片的傑瑞德·雷托被獲頒該屆最差男主角，然而傑瑞德·雷托亦入圍[[評論家選擇協會|評論家選擇協會]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2021/12/critics-choice-awards-film-nominations-2022-1234889884/ |title=Critics Choice Awards Film Nominations Led By 'Belfast' And 'West Side Story' |first=Pete |last=Hammond |date=2021-12-13 |work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |access-date=2022-02-08 |archive-date=2021-12-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211219100808/https://deadline.com/2021/12/critics-choice-awards-film-nominations-2022-1234889884/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和{{le|美國演員工會|Screen Actors Guild}}獎的最佳男配角<ref>{{cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2022/01/sag-awards-nominations-2020-list-film-tv-nominees-screen-actors-guild-1234908756/ |title=SAG Awards Nominations: 'House Of Gucci', 'Power Of The Dog', 'Succession', 'Ted Lasso' Top Lists |first=Patrick |last=Hipes |work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] |date=2022-01-12 |access-date=2022-02-08 |archive-date=2022-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220119044627/https://deadline.com/2022/01/sag-awards-nominations-2020-list-film-tv-nominees-screen-actors-guild-1234908756/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。傑瑞德·雷托獲頒金酸莓獎的事蹟引起《[[影音俱樂部|The Avocado]]》影評人的批評，稱其「他也不配出現在這」<ref name="Avocado">{{cite web |url=https://the-avocado.org/2022/01/21/scott-looks-at-the-razzie-ballot-year-4-did-ben-affleck-run-over-the-razzies-cat-or-something/ |title=Scott Looks at the Razzie Ballot Year 4: Did Ben Affleck Run Over the Razzie's Cat or Something? |author=THEIMMORTANSCOTT |work=The Avocado |date=2022-01-21 |access-date=2022-01-22 |archive-date=2022-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220206045350/https://the-avocado.org/2022/01/21/scott-looks-at-the-razzie-ballot-year-4-did-ben-affleck-run-over-the-razzies-cat-or-something/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

